# Portal Web Rules

## i18n

- All user-visible strings must use i18n translations
- Import `useLocale` hook for client components
- Translation files in `packages/i18n/locales/{vi,en}/<namespace>.json`
- Key pattern: `namespace.context.element`

## Components

- Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/`
- Shared layout components in `@/components/layout/`
- Feature components in `@/components/<feature>/`
- Use Lucide React for icons

## Data Fetching

- Use Server Components for initial data fetch where possible
- Client components for interactive features (forms, filters, real-time)
- API calls go through `@/lib/api.ts` (to be created)
- Never call backend services directly from components

## Viewer Integration

- OHIF viewer URL configured via `NEXT_PUBLIC_OHIF_URL` env var
- Deep-link format: `{OHIF_URL}/ohif/viewer?StudyInstanceUIDs=...&taskId=...&caseId=...`
- Always open viewer in new tab (`target="_blank"`)
